revision.text: ==English== ===Etymology=== From {{m|grc|ξιφία}}, from {{m|grc|ξίφος||sword}} {{suffix|en||oid}}. ===Adjective=== {{en-adj}} # {{lb|en|zoology}} resembling or related to the genus ''[[Xiphias]]'' (swordfish). # {{lb|en|zoology}} resembling or related to the family [[Xiphiidae]] (a group of [[fish]]). ===Noun=== {{en-noun}} # {{lb|en|zoology}} Any member of the genus ''[[Xiphias]]'' or family [[Xiphiidae]]. [[Category:en:Scombroids]]
